edge cases:

adding learners or mentors

- adding exisitng learners
- adding existing mentors
- adding learners as mentors
- adding mentor as learners

edge case at the time of school creation
- slug should be unique
- name should be non-empty
- slug should be non-empty

during addition of team member
- should not already exist in the school

adding courses to cohort
- no courses exist
- courses already added should not be shown
- no more courses available that can be added since all courses have been added - different from no courses available in the first place